dc_title_s: Trails Fond du Lac County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data group represents trails for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'IceAgeTrail', 'NonCountyTrails', and 'Trails'. [IceAgeTrail: This data set is an ArcInfo line coverage representing existing Ice Age Trail in Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
